        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"><b>Is this soloable for a lvl 51 necro ?</b> Yes</P><P><b>Who is PH ?</b> Any of the spectral type mobs.  Xal isn't to rare.</P><P><b>Can i invis all the way to his spawn point ?</b> Maybe, see next question.</P><P><b>ITU or regular invis ?</b> Yes, both.  Use regular invis to get to the "crossroads" (note: some strathbone spiders DO see invis), then ITU to get to the church.</P><P><b>Is casting time same as normal cast of invoke fear or higher ?</b>  Higher, I think it's 6 seconds.</P><P><b>Is the effect right clickable ?</b> Yes.</P><P><b>Does it have to be equipped to use ?</b> Not sure, I don't think so.</P><P></P><P>--Nergal Teir'Draconis, Children of the Phoenix (Tunare)<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
