        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">The staff casts invoke fear at 7.5 seconds and normal invoke fear casts at 2.5 seconds.  The thing is that Invoke Fear (casted) has a 7 second recyle time.  The staff can be used instantly after each cast.  So its a matter of what you prefer.  Fast cast/slow recyle or Fast recyle/slow cast, free 100 mana, and spell slot.  Or, better yet, cast fear yourself and, when you think the duration is about up, use the staff.  Might be pretty helpful against mobs that take awhile to kill, like giants. <img src=icon_smile.gif border=0 align=middle></P><P>~Taleldar Dreamslayer<BR>50th Necromancer of<BR>Morell Thule<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
